<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM7.1.7">
<l>katiyē lillainiṉ ṉaruḷallate ṉakku</l>
<l>nitiyē tirunīr malainittilat tottē</l>
<l>patiyē paravit toḻumtoṇṭarta makkuk</l>
<l>katiyē yuṉṉaikkaṇ ṭukoṇṭuyntoḻin tēṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Salvation is not possible for me without your grace;</l>
<l>Treasure, pearl cluster of Tirunīrmalai,</l>
<l>Master, salvation for us, your servants who worship, praising [you],</l>
<l>Seeing you for myself [and] obtaining bliss, I was at ease.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
